title: Kritika Chaos Unleashed v2.7.1 (Android)
description:
This is full updated client Kritika : Chaos Unleashed v2.7.1
No mod, nothing added, and 100% clean.

How to :
1. Unpack the file "com.gamevil.kritikamobile.android.google.global.normal.7z"
without creating a new folder,
2. Copy extracted folder "com.gamevil.kritikamobile.android.google.global.normal"
into your Android device storage: >Androiddata
3. Copy "kritika271.apk" into your Android device storage in any folder where you place apk files or just paste into Download folder
4. Before you install, better clean older version if you have installed before, clean the Kritika chace and data then uninstall.
5. Install the apk "Kritika271.apk", after finish you can start the game, login or create new account
